snippet.title: Cattle Country Gameplay Trailer - Convergence Showcase
snippet.description:
A brand new trailer for cosy cowboy farming sim Cattle Country, announcing the open beta date. As revealed during the Convergence Showcase. 

Wishlist the game here: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2818150/Cattle_Country/
